Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なんだっていまから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.19,0:23:55.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}できちゃいそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:57.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me　かならず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:02.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ほんとうの未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:05.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そばにあること
